sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App
    participant Server
    participant Database

    User->>App: Open File
    App->>App: Detect File Type

    alt Markdown File
        App->>App: Render Markdown
    else Mermaid File
        App->>App: Render Mermaid
    end

    User->>App: Export
    App->>Server: Generate Export
    Server->>Database: Save Metadata
    Database-->>Server: Confirmation
    Server-->>App: Export Ready
    App-->>User: Download File
